# Roblox Open Cloud API key (Creator Hub → Open Cloud → API Keys).
# Required for gamepasses, dev products, subscription reads.
# Scopes needed (per feature):
#   game-pass:read, game-pass:write
#   developer-product:read, developer-product:write
#   universe.subscription-product.subscription:read
#   legacy-universe.badge:write, legacy-badge:manage
RBX_MONET_API_KEY=

# Optional. Required only to push badge updates (rbxmonet sync on [badges.*]),
# because legacy *.roblox.com write endpoints need a logged-in session cookie
# in addition to the x-api-key + x-csrf-token flow.
#
# ⚠️ DO NOT COMMIT. This is account-takeover material. If leaked, log out of
# every session at https://www.roblox.com/my/account#!/security to rotate it.
#
# Get it from a logged-in browser: DevTools → Application → Cookies →
# https://www.roblox.com → .ROBLOSECURITY → Value.
RBX_MONET_ROBLOSECURITY=
